+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|
|  Author:  Cor Bosman (roundcube@wa.ter.net)
|  Plugin:  listcommands
|  Version: 1.1
|  Purpose: Perform mailinglist tasks from roundcube
|
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+

listcommands adds a set of commands to the headers of your email to
manage mailinglist emails. This lets you easily subscribe, unsubscribe,
check the archives etc.

Installation
------------

Copy the plugin to your plugin folder
Add the plugin to your config/main.inc.php
